-- New York City Subway Bomb Plot Suspect to Plead Guilty, His Lawyer Says
-- Patricia Hurtado
-- 2010-04-23T17:43:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/new-york-city-subway-bomb-plot-suspect-to-plead-guilty-his-lawyer-says.html

          
          
             Zarein Ahmedzay, accused of
conspiring with admitted terrorist Najibullah Zazi in an al-
Qaeda plot to detonate bombs on New York City subways, will
plead guilty today to conspiracy and supporting terrorists, his
lawyer said during the plea hearing in Brooklyn federal court.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Hurtado in New York at 
 pathurtado@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        